com.intel.device.impl.phone.sensor.model

Class PhoneSensorThreadWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.device.impl.phone.sensor.model.PhoneSensorThreadWrapper

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class PhoneSensorThreadWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class uses a thread-containment pattern to wrap a phone sensor and execute it on a background thread.

        public void shutdown()
